trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class encapsulates the transport security settings for queued transports.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> encapsula as configurações de segurança do transporte para transportes na fila.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The existing instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class, to be used in initializing the new instance.
trans-unit.target: A instância existente da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> a ser usada ao inicializar a nova instância.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class, using an existing instance.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> usando uma instância existente.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="other" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="other" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can authenticate messages that are sent to message queues that require authentication, or messages can explicitly request authentication.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ pode autenticar mensagens enviadas para filas de mensagens que exigem autenticação ou mensagens explicitamente podem solicitar a autenticação.

trans-unit.source: The default authentication mode is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.
trans-unit.target: O modo de autenticação padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> values.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é um dos valores <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can encrypt messages on the wire when transferring messages between message queue managers.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ pode criptografar mensagens na conexão durante a transferência de mensagens entre os gerenciadores de fila de mensagem.

trans-unit.source: The default encryption algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.
trans-unit.target: O algoritmo de criptografia padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> values.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é um dos valores <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.

trans-unit.source: The default protection level is <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.
trans-unit.target: O nível de proteção padrão é <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> values.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é um dos valores <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" />.

trans-unit.source: The default hash algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm.Sha1>.
trans-unit.target: O algoritmo de hash padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm.Sha1>.

trans-unit.target: O valor não é um dos valores <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" />.
